@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantFontColor Black
  ActorFontColor Black
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API\nGET /api/meters/building/:buildingId" as API
participant "Database\nTable: MeterInfo" as DB
User->UI: Select a meter to view
UI->API: Request meter details
API->DB: Retrieve meters for the building
DB-->API: Return meter data
API-->UI: Return meter details
UI-->User: Display meter details

@enduml
